Class.ClassComment:
TypedFormat /** * Derby interface for identifying the format id for the stored form of an object. Objects of different classes may have the same format id if:
  • The objects read and write the same stored forms.
  • The object's getTypeId() method returns the same identifier.
  • The objects support all the interfaces the type implies.
*/

Method.MethodComment: /** * Get a universally unique identifier for the type of this object. * @return The identifier. (A UUID stuffed in an arrayof 16 bytes). */
